projects.name: FinDash
projects.description: Developed a dynamic Finance Dashboard app using the MERN stack, incorporating Machine Learning to provide predictive analytics. The frontend is built with Vite, Redux Toolkit, Material UI, and Recharts for an interactive user experience. Implemented a robust backend with Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB for seamless data management and real-time insights.

projects.name: CraftResume - An AI Resume Builder Tool
projects.description: CraftResume is an AI-powered resume builder that streamlines the creation of professional resumes using React.js, Vite for fast development, Strapi as a headless CMS, Clerk for user authentication, and Tailwind CSS for sleek, responsive design. With seamless integration and a user-friendly interface, CraftResume ensures that job seekers can easily create, edit, and delete their resumes, enhancing their chances of landing the perfect job.

experiences.description: Developed scripts using Python and used a custom-trained YOLOv8 model, enabling real-time identification of leader-follower pairs of detected vehicles in video data. Engineered data visualization components and CSV file to display the identified leader-follower pairs and their relative positions over time, providing insights into traffic dynamics. Worked in an agile environment, adapting to changing requirements and collaborating closely with mentors and peers to achieve project milestones.
